plot: The Doctor makes one last stop before his death to see an old friend. But people are disappearing, there are reports of a silver rat and metal men are lurking in the shadows.

After traveling for 200 years and leaving messages for Amy Pond across time and space, the Doctor realizes his time is up, its time to settle down and accept his future at Lake Silencio. . . . . .But not before one last goodbye. The Doctor travels to England and visits Craig and Sophie, who are now happily married and struggling with parenthood. Not everything is well, as the Doctor soon finds himself miraculously working at a shop and battling Cybermen.—Trevor Alvis

Traveling on his own the Doctor decides to visits his old friends Craig and Sophie who are now the proud parents of a newborn baby. Craig is on his own as the Doctor arrives and the new dad is just a bit overwhelmed as he struggles to learn new parenting skills. The Doctor has him beat hands down as far as parenting goes but while out shopping together, the Doctor realizes that they are all in great danger - from the Cybermen. Meanwhile, Kovarian re-appears and kidnaps River Song as the Doctor's final day approaches.—garykmcd
